description:
Are you an influencer? Did you know you can make a huge impact on the world? Discover how the power of influence can be attained by anyone who desires to serve God.
In this enlightening presentation, Scott Mayer discusses the potential each of us possesses as influencers, drawing inspiration from historical figures who, despite facing criticism, left a profound mark on the world. As Christians, we are called to be the salt of the earth, and that may mean making conscious choices that are in opposition to worldly influences and beliefs. Join Scott as he explores Gods word and inspires us  to use our  influence for godly purposes!
